{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":6960,"text":"Now..."},{"time":9200,"text":"let's go back in time."},{"time":12560,"text":"It's 1974."},{"time":17960,"text":"There is the gallery somewhere"},{"time":21880,"text":"in the world,"},{"time":25080,"text":"and there is a young girl, age 23,"},{"time":28400,"text":"standing in the middle of the space."},{"time":32759,"text":"In the front of her is a table."},{"time":37000,"text":"On the table there are 76 objects"},{"time":42720,"text":"for pleasure and for pain."},{"time":46520,"text":"Some of the objects are"},{"time":48720,"text":"a glass of water, a coat, a shoe, a rose."},{"time":55160,"text":"But also the knife,\nthe razor blade, the hammer"},{"time":61800,"text":"and the pistol with one bullet."},{"time":66240,"text":"There are instructions which say,"},{"time":69240,"text":"\"I'm an object."},{"time":71000,"text":"You can use everything on the table on me."},{"time":74360,"text":"I'm taking all responsibility --\neven killing me."},{"time":78920,"text":"And the time is six hours.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":83600,"text":"The beginning of this\nperformance was easy."},{"time":88280,"text":"People would give me\nthe glass of water to drink,"},{"time":91880,"text":"they'd give me the rose."},{"time":94120,"text":"But very soon after,"},{"time":96920,"text":"there was a man who took the scissors\nand cut my clothes,"},{"time":100440,"text":"and then they took the thorns of the rose\nand stuck them in my stomach."},{"time":104920,"text":"Somebody took the razor blade\nand cut my neck and drank the blood,"},{"time":109960,"text":"and I still have the scar."},{"time":112720,"text":"The women would tell the men what to do."},{"time":116000,"text":"And the men didn't rape me\nbecause it was just a normal opening,"},{"time":120840,"text":"and it was all public,"},{"time":122560,"text":"and they were with their wives."},{"time":124960,"text":"They carried me around\nand put me on the table,"},{"time":127240,"text":"and put the knife between my legs."},{"time":129160,"text":"And somebody took the pistol and bullet\nand put it against my temple."},{"time":133560,"text":"And another person took the pistol\nand they started a fight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138920,"text":"And after six hours were finished,"},{"time":141680,"text":"I..."},{"time":144200,"text":"started walking towards the public."},{"time":147360,"text":"I was a mess."},{"time":148600,"text":"I was half-naked, I was full of blood\nand tears were running down my face."},{"time":154040,"text":"And everybody escaped, they just ran away."},{"time":157280,"text":"They could not confront myself,\nwith myself as a normal human being."},{"time":162760,"text":"And then --"},{"time":165080,"text":"what happened"},{"time":167240,"text":"is I went to the hotel,\nit was at two in the morning."},{"time":173080,"text":"And"},{"time":175680,"text":"I looked at myself in the mirror,"},{"time":178520,"text":"and I had a piece of gray hair."},{"time":184080,"text":"Alright --"},{"time":186000,"text":"please take off your blindfolds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190760,"text":"Welcome to the performance world."},{"time":193520,"text":"First of all, let's explain\nwhat the performance is."},{"time":197840,"text":"So many artists,\nso many different explanations,"},{"time":200400,"text":"but my explanation\nfor performance is very simple."},{"time":203640,"text":"Performance is a mental\nand physical construction"},{"time":208240,"text":"that the performer makes\nin a specific time"},{"time":211080,"text":"in a space in front of an audience"},{"time":214400,"text":"and then energy dialogue happens."},{"time":217280,"text":"The audience and the performer\nmake the piece together."},{"time":221600,"text":"And the difference between\nperformance and theater is huge."},{"time":226240,"text":"In the theater, the knife is not a knife"},{"time":229720,"text":"and the blood is just ketchup."},{"time":232040,"text":"In the performance,\nthe blood is the material,"},{"time":236600,"text":"and the razor blade or knife is the tool."},{"time":239920,"text":"It's all about being there\nin the real time,"},{"time":243840,"text":"and you can't rehearse performance,"},{"time":245720,"text":"because you can't do many\nof these types of things twice -- ever."},{"time":251360,"text":"Which is very important,\nthe performance is --"},{"time":253880,"text":"you know, all human beings\nare always afraid of very simple things."},{"time":258200,"text":"We're afraid of suffering,\nwe're afraid of pain,"},{"time":261600,"text":"we're afraid of mortality."},{"time":264240,"text":"So what I'm doing --"},{"time":265520,"text":"I'm staging these kinds of fears\nin front of the audience."},{"time":269760,"text":"I'm using your energy,"},{"time":271960,"text":"and with this energy I can go\nand push my body as far as I can."},{"time":277760,"text":"And then I liberate myself\nfrom these fears."},{"time":281360,"text":"And I'm your mirror."},{"time":282680,"text":"If I can do this for myself,\nyou can do it for you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286720,"text":"After Belgrade, where I was born,"},{"time":288800,"text":"I went to Amsterdam."},{"time":291440,"text":"And you know, I've been doing performances"},{"time":294080,"text":"since the last 40 years."},{"time":296360,"text":"And here I met Ulay,"},{"time":297960,"text":"and he was the person\nI actually fell in love with."},{"time":301360,"text":"And we made, for 12 years,\nperformances together."},{"time":304520,"text":"You know the knife\nand the pistols and the bullets,"},{"time":307800,"text":"I exchange into love and trust."},{"time":310760,"text":"So to do this kind work\nyou have to trust the person completely"},{"time":314400,"text":"because this arrow\nis pointing to my heart."},{"time":317440,"text":"So, heart beating and adrenaline\nis rushing and so on,"},{"time":321800,"text":"is about trust, is about total trust\nto another human being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327320,"text":"Our relationship was 12 years,"},{"time":329560,"text":"and we worked on so many subjects,\nboth male and female energy."},{"time":333440,"text":"And as every relationship\ncomes to an end, ours went too."},{"time":337600,"text":"We didn't make phone calls\nlike normal human beings do"},{"time":341280,"text":"and say, you know, \"This is over.\""},{"time":343280,"text":"We walked the Great Wall\nof China to say goodbye."},{"time":346640,"text":"I started at the Yellow Sea,\nand he started from the Gobi Desert."},{"time":351200,"text":"We walked, each of us, three months,"},{"time":354600,"text":"two and a half thousand kilometers."},{"time":356800,"text":"It was the mountains, it was difficult."},{"time":358800,"text":"It was climbing, it was ruins."},{"time":361160,"text":"It was, you know, going through\nthe 12 Chinese provinces,"},{"time":364280,"text":"this was before China was open in '87."},{"time":368120,"text":"And we succeeded to meet in the middle"},{"time":371680,"text":"to say goodbye."},{"time":374320,"text":"And then our relationship stopped."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376560,"text":"And now, it completely changed\nhow I see the public."},{"time":381280,"text":"And one very important piece\nI made in those days"},{"time":384440,"text":"was \"Balkan Baroque.\""},{"time":386440,"text":"And this was the time of the Balkan Wars,"},{"time":389160,"text":"and I wanted to create\nsome very strong, charismatic image,"},{"time":392720,"text":"something that could serve\nfor any war at any time,"},{"time":396040,"text":"because the Balkan Wars are now finished,\nbut there's always some war, somewhere."},{"time":400080,"text":"So here I am washing"},{"time":402080,"text":"two and a half thousand\ndead, big, bloody cow bones."},{"time":405880,"text":"You can't wash the blood,\nyou never can wash shame off the wars."},{"time":409440,"text":"So I'm washing this six hours, six days,\nand wars are coming off these bones,"},{"time":414040,"text":"and becoming possible --\nan unbearable smell."},{"time":417640,"text":"But then something stays in the memory."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420520,"text":"I want to show you the one\nwho really changed my life,"},{"time":423280,"text":"and this was the performance in MoMa,\nwhich I just recently made."},{"time":427440,"text":"This performance --\nwhen I said to the curator,"},{"time":430800,"text":"\"I'm just going to sit at the chair,"},{"time":432800,"text":"and there will be\nan empty chair at the front,"},{"time":435360,"text":"and anybody from the public\ncan come and sit as long as they want.\""},{"time":438880,"text":"The curator said to me,"},{"time":440120,"text":"\"That's ridiculous, you know,\nthis is New York,"},{"time":442800,"text":"this chair will be empty,"},{"time":444040,"text":"nobody has time to sit in front of you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":445969,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":447160,"text":"But I sit for three months."},{"time":449080,"text":"And I sit everyday, eight hours --"},{"time":451040,"text":"the opening of the museum --"},{"time":452440,"text":"and 10 hours on Friday\nwhen the museum is open 10 hours,"},{"time":455360,"text":"and I never move."},{"time":456558,"text":"And I removed the table\nand I'm still sitting,"},{"time":459440,"text":"and this changed everything."},{"time":461960,"text":"This performance,\nmaybe 10 or 15 years ago --"},{"time":464320,"text":"nothing would have happened."},{"time":465760,"text":"But the need of people to actually\nexperience something different,"},{"time":470680,"text":"the public was not anymore the group --"},{"time":472800,"text":"relation was one to one."},{"time":475160,"text":"I was watching these people,\nthey would come and sit in front of me,"},{"time":478920,"text":"but they would have to wait\nfor hours and hours and hours"},{"time":481640,"text":"to get to this position,"},{"time":482823,"text":"and finally, they sit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484400,"text":"And what happened?"},{"time":486440,"text":"They are observed by the other people,"},{"time":488600,"text":"they're photographed,\nthey're filmed by the camera,"},{"time":491200,"text":"they're observed by me"},{"time":492600,"text":"and they have nowhere to escape\nexcept in themselves."},{"time":496240,"text":"And that makes a difference."},{"time":497840,"text":"There was so much pain and loneliness,"},{"time":499680,"text":"there's so much incredible things\nwhen you look in somebody else's eyes,"},{"time":503800,"text":"because in the gaze\nwith that total stranger,"},{"time":506800,"text":"that you never even say one word --\neverything happened."},{"time":510200,"text":"And I understood when I stood up\nfrom that chair after three months,"},{"time":515200,"text":"I am not the same anymore."},{"time":516799,"text":"And I understood\nthat I have a very strong mission,"},{"time":519600,"text":"that I have to communicate this experience"},{"time":522880,"text":"to everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524159,"text":"And this is how, for me, was born the idea"},{"time":527000,"text":"to have an institute\nof immaterial performing arts."},{"time":531320,"text":"Because thinking about immateriality,"},{"time":534240,"text":"performance is time-based art."},{"time":535720,"text":"It's not like a painting."},{"time":537080,"text":"You have the painting on the wall,\nthe next day it's there."},{"time":539880,"text":"Performance, if you are missing it,\nyou only have the memory,"},{"time":544600,"text":"or the story of somebody else telling you,"},{"time":546960,"text":"but you actually missed the whole thing."},{"time":548920,"text":"So you have to be there."},{"time":550160,"text":"And in my point,\nif you talk about immaterial art,"},{"time":553080,"text":"music is the highest --\nabsolutely highest art of all,"},{"time":556480,"text":"because it's the most immaterial."},{"time":558280,"text":"And then after this is performance,\nand then everything else."},{"time":561162,"text":"That's my subjective way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562720,"text":"This institute is going to happen\nin Hudson, upstate New York,"},{"time":566640,"text":"and we are trying to build\nwith Rem Koolhaas, an idea."},{"time":569960,"text":"And it's very simple."},{"time":571240,"text":"If you want to get experience,\nyou have to give me your time."},{"time":575920,"text":"You have to sign the contract\nbefore you enter the building,"},{"time":579040,"text":"that you will spend there\na full six hours,"},{"time":581920,"text":"you have to give me your word of honor."},{"time":584600,"text":"It's something so old-fashioned,"},{"time":586520,"text":"but if you don't respect your own\nword of honor and you leave before --"},{"time":589880,"text":"that's not my problem."},{"time":591120,"text":"But it's six hours, the experience."},{"time":593640,"text":"And then after you finish,\nyou get a certificate of accomplishment,"},{"time":596807,"text":"so get home and frame it if you want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598880,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":599920,"text":"This is orientation hall."},{"time":601280,"text":"The public comes in, and the first thing\nyou have to do is dress in lab coats."},{"time":605800,"text":"It's this importance"},{"time":607040,"text":"of stepping from being\njust a viewer into experimenter."},{"time":611280,"text":"And then you go to the lockers"},{"time":613720,"text":"and you put your watch,\nyour iPhone, your iPod, your computer"},{"time":617040,"text":"and everything digital, electronic."},{"time":619360,"text":"And you are getting free time\nfor yourself for the first time."},{"time":623720,"text":"Because there is nothing\nwrong with technology,"},{"time":627120,"text":"our approach to technology is wrong."},{"time":629480,"text":"We are losing the time\nwe have for ourselves."},{"time":632200,"text":"This is an institute\nto actually give you back this time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635520,"text":"So what you do here,"},{"time":636800,"text":"first you start slow walking,\nyou start slowing down."},{"time":639920,"text":"You're going back to simplicity."},{"time":641880,"text":"After slow walking, you're going\nto learn how to drink water --"},{"time":645520,"text":"very simple, drinking water\nfor maybe half an hour."},{"time":649640,"text":"After this, you're going to\nthe magnet chamber,"},{"time":651960,"text":"where you're going to create\nsome magnet streams on your body."},{"time":655880,"text":"Then after this,\nyou go to crystal chamber."},{"time":658360,"text":"After crystal chamber,\nyou go to eye-gazing chamber,"},{"time":661160,"text":"after eye-gazing chamber, you go to\na chamber where you are lying down."},{"time":665280,"text":"So it's the three basic positions\nof the human body,"},{"time":667760,"text":"sitting, standing and lying."},{"time":669120,"text":"And slow walking."},{"time":670680,"text":"And there is a sound chamber."},{"time":672520,"text":"And then after you've seen all of this,"},{"time":674880,"text":"and prepared yourself\nmentally and physically,"},{"time":677047,"text":"then you are ready to see\nsomething with a long duration,"},{"time":679738,"text":"like in immaterial art."},{"time":682120,"text":"It can be music, it can be opera,\nit can be a theater piece,"},{"time":686000,"text":"it can be film, it can be video dance."},{"time":688920,"text":"You go to the long duration chairs\nbecause now you are comfortable."},{"time":692760,"text":"In the long duration chairs,"},{"time":694160,"text":"you're transported to the big place\nwhere you're going to see the work."},{"time":697880,"text":"And if you fall asleep,"},{"time":699120,"text":"which is very possible\nbecause it's been a long day,"},{"time":701680,"text":"you're going to be\ntransported to the parking lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":705800,"text":"And you know, sleeping is very important."},{"time":708640,"text":"In sleeping, you're still receiving art."},{"time":711440,"text":"So in the parking lot you stay\nfor a certain amount of time,"},{"time":715160,"text":"and then after this\nyou just, you know, go back,"},{"time":718440,"text":"you see more of the things you like to see"},{"time":720800,"text":"or go home with your certificate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723280,"text":"So this institute right now is virtual."},{"time":726720,"text":"Right now, I am just\nmaking my institute in Brazil,"},{"time":729600,"text":"then it's going to be in Australia,"},{"time":731291,"text":"then it's coming here,\nto Canada and everywhere."},{"time":734440,"text":"And this is to experience\na kind of simple method,"},{"time":737960,"text":"how you go back to simplicity\nin your own life."},{"time":740880,"text":"Counting rice will be another thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":745680,"text":"You know, if you count rice\nyou can make life, too."},{"time":748200,"text":"How to count rice for six hours?"},{"time":750400,"text":"It's incredibly important."},{"time":752120,"text":"You know, you go through this whole range\nof being bored, being angry,"},{"time":756280,"text":"being completely frustrated, not finishing\nthe amount of rice you're counting."},{"time":760760,"text":"And then this unbelievable\namount of peace you get"},{"time":763560,"text":"when satisfying work is finished --"},{"time":766040,"text":"or counting sand in the desert."},{"time":768600,"text":"Or having the sound-isolated situation --"},{"time":772120,"text":"that you have headphones,\nthat you don't hear anything,"},{"time":774720,"text":"and you're just there\ntogether without sound,"},{"time":777440,"text":"with the people experiencing silence,\njust the simple silence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782320,"text":"We are always doing things\nwe like in our life."},{"time":786560,"text":"And this is why you're not changing."},{"time":788840,"text":"You do things in life --"},{"time":790320,"text":"it's just nothing happens\nif you always do things the same way."},{"time":794200,"text":"But my method is to do things\nI'm afraid of, the things I fear,"},{"time":799320,"text":"the things I don't know,"},{"time":800840,"text":"to go to territory\nthat nobody's ever been."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803720,"text":"And then also to include the failure."},{"time":806600,"text":"I think failure is important"},{"time":808360,"text":"because if you go,\nif you experiment, you can fail."},{"time":812120,"text":"If you don't go into that area\nand you don't fail,"},{"time":814800,"text":"you are actually repeating yourself\nover and over again."},{"time":818320,"text":"And I think that human beings\nright now need a change,"},{"time":822160,"text":"and the only change to be made\nis a personal level change."},{"time":826280,"text":"You have to make the change on yourself."},{"time":828880,"text":"Because the only way\nto change consciousness"},{"time":831400,"text":"and to change the world around us,"},{"time":833440,"text":"is to start with yourself."},{"time":835160,"text":"It's so easy to criticize\nhow it's different,"},{"time":837680,"text":"the things in the world\nand they're not right,"},{"time":839847,"text":"and the governments are corrupted\nand there's hunger in the world"},{"time":843120,"text":"and there's wars -- the killing."},{"time":846600,"text":"But what we do on the personal level --"},{"time":849200,"text":"what is our contribution\nto this whole thing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":852960,"text":"Can you turn to your neighbor,\nthe one you don't know,"},{"time":856080,"text":"and look at them for two full minutes\nin their eyes, right now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":861840,"text":"(Chatter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":866360,"text":"I'm asking two minutes\nof your time, that's so little."},{"time":870280,"text":"Breathe slowly, don't try to blink,\ndon't be self-conscious."},{"time":875640,"text":"Be relaxed."},{"time":877280,"text":"And just look a complete\nstranger in your eyes, in his eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883520,"text":"(Silence)"},{"time":923040,"text":"Thank you for trusting me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925720,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":933360,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thank you."},{"time":936360,"text":"Thank you so much."}]}]}